  <div class="container" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 60px">
    <p class="section-label">Our Commitment</p>
    <h1>Ethics<br>Statement</h1>
    <p class="date">Effective May 29, 2026. At Brioo, ethical conduct isn't a marketing position — it is the foundation every single decision is built on.</p>
  </div>
