<div class="ethics-layout">
  <p class="section-label reveal">What We Stand For</p>
  <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.05;max-width:700px;margin-bottom:32px">Six principles we publicly commit to — and hold ourselves accountable to.</h2>
  <div class="ethics-grid">
    <div class="ethics-card reveal"><div class="num">01</div><h3>Radical Honesty</h3><p>We never fabricate follower counts, engagement metrics, or case studies. We don't use bots or fake accounts. We are transparent about our size, our process, and our results — even when they are imperfect. A creator deserves an honest agency.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
    <div class="ethics-card reveal" data-delay="0.08"><div class="num">02</div><h3>Fair Compensation, Always</h3><p>We never ask creators to work "for exposure." Every campaign includes a paid contract with clear terms. We negotiate on behalf of creators to ensure they receive fair market rates — and we only take our cut after they receive theirs.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
    <div class="ethics-card reveal" data-delay="0.1"><div class="num">03</div><h3>No Harmful Industries</h3><p>Gambling, alcohol, adult content, weapons, interest-based finance, deceptive products — all rejected without exception. We will turn down commission rather than broker a deal that could harm our creators' audience or violate our ethical standards.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
    <div class="ethics-card reveal" data-delay="0.12"><div class="num">04</div><h3>Transparency with Data</h3><p>We provide honest reporting to brands — including real engagement rates, reach, clicks, and conversions. We do not hide underperformance. We use the data to improve, never to mislead. Truth earns more trust than spin ever will.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
    <div class="ethics-card reveal" data-delay="0.14"><div class="num">05</div><h3>Long-Term Over Short-Term</h3><p>We prioritise trust over commissions. If a deal does not genuinely benefit both the creator and the brand, we will not facilitate it. We believe that ethical business compounds over time — and unsustainable shortcuts cost more than they're worth.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
    <div class="ethics-card reveal" data-delay="0.16"><div class="num">06</div><h3>Full Accountability</h3><p>If we make a mistake, we own it. If a campaign underperforms, we analyse why and adjust our process. We welcome feedback from all partners. We do not hide behind fine print or deflect responsibility. This statement is a public commitment we invite you to hold us to.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="ethics-pledge reveal"><blockquote>"If you wouldn't recommend it to your own audience, we won't pitch it to theirs."</blockquote><p class="attr">The Brioo Standard — applied to every deal, every time</p></div>
